headline.main: Texas Police Officials Reassigned Amid Leaked Video, Records
headline.print_headline: Texas Police Officials Reassigned Amid Leaked Video, Records

lead_paragraph: Two police commanders in Texas have been temporarily replaced as investigators determine who leaked police video and other material in the controversial arrest of a black woman and her daughters by a white Fort Worth police officer.
